item.title: CVE-2013-1951|2024-08-06T15:20:37.304Z -- ikimedia%20foundation -- mediawiki
item.description: A cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability in MediaWiki before 1.19.5 and 1.20.x before 1.20.4 and allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary web script or HTML via Lua function names.
